### SSH key

```sh
  # setup ssh key
mkdir ~/.ssh
ln -s ~/Library/Mobile\ Documents/com\~apple\~CloudDocs/ssh/* ~/.ssh/
chmod 600 ~/.ssh/config
chmod 600 ~/.ssh/id_*
```

